{"tid":1479460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（鴨記）身在藍營，心在黃地 2","createTime":"2019-08-17T02:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T02:29:08.000Z","uid":105651,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0c5188a6ddf8631a0c25ca611a1935b814c9d4","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"由於冇咩人推，我要在po<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rd6XO3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frd6XO3b.jpg&h=435fdb81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DioLduS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDioLduS.jpg&h=bbc8b260&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MaSv83d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMaSv83d.jpg&h=15d3b07f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家知道雖然呢間公司大部分都係藍絲！<br />\n但都有不少黃絲，一間存在深藍，深黃員工既一間公司！<br />\n我地係一班唔會同流合污既員工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 今次見到AA 擅自擴大來自法庭的禁制令，封左好多出入口！對好多人造成不便！無論遊客或者員工！<br />\n我地員工都想問候佢_親戚！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實大家可以睇反禁制令，其實有d地方冇話唔比市民入架，肯出去企門口既鴨🦆記，一係藍，一係蝦9 d新人（白板），一係被逼，仲有一班認真撚藍絲！我部門好多唔願意，已經射波！<br />\n所以歡迎大家入機場購物睇戲！或者接我地收工😏"},{"pid":"27507b2d9b32475c2d3692ea70371a4d34032ad4","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"歡迎你問我答"},{"pid":"eb7017f7af6e8d3d7251cad31e62bfd351e4e317","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"41e22dcd95a7645aed9efe446b0bf2cf5760fadd","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"d1a888982281983f398d90de2455673d82483b22","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:18:31.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"2244c128735205bd3a0efd2011ef9685cbd8bc65","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:18:41.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"9ec78950ebab0eae0e7e40f8f25914d9140c5c22","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"9b471bdb0cf7411370e215db20d5e069489d9537","tid":1479460,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"e028e51c2427d74ea9cf6658